ygData.messageBody:
Try roaming and looking for Goblins walking around. Also Giant Spiders
might still con BLUE for you and you might be able to find a blue skeleton
or 2, don't try to solo a skel that cons BLACK or YELLOW! The main thing
is don't CAMP and the goblin camp, you can usually kill stuff quicker
running around killing stuff. Just CON everything and if it is blue try
it. (look out for the lowlands basilisk though cus it STUNS)
Good Luck

P.S. your best bet is to get in a big party and kill 'the goblin wizards'
and stuff like that.
